     assertParse(

+      diagnostics: expectedDiagnostics,
+      fixedSource: "_ = nil\n{ return nil }"
+    )

+      "_ = 11️⃣ { return 1 }",
+      diagnostics: expectedDiagnostics,
+      fixedSource: "_ = 1\n{ return 1 }"
